---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout>


<main class="pt-24">
<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative min-h-[600px] flex items-center px-gutter py-section-padding-desktop">
<div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 overflow-hidden">
<img alt="Architectural view of modern school" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-20" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuClhIZrUkDjnUwwuXpx7QB3RzRZ2qxzwXc6_jqm2cHKpBj8AVT7vf71KqCy38Vc5luaCvHWPntMotcOEw97KG8UludrSF6O1DgccbWLHCJdtll-QxIibsy5pCXpx8g7JCtvCo-VEJ2EGiH-nBPV5ItwJmNIDqIyR9MecPfvw_a-6pfa4D7QIPPP1gBHUnNI3uVfuV79_cBzW87P_Jgvoh-_4rvS6LFrZyR4wxJADtRIHqv4rmN3HrrIymlLz40DE4uhY9p0uSxwkGs">
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-background via-background/80 to-transparent"></div>
</div>
<div class="container mx-auto relative z-10 max-w-container-max">
<div class="max-w-3xl animate-fade-in-up">
<span class="inline-block px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary-container text-on-tertiary-container font-label-caps mb-6">KURIKULUM &amp; PROGRAM</span>
<h1 class="font-display-lg text-display-lg-mobile md:text-display-lg text-primary mb-6 leading-tight">
                        Eksplorasi Potensi Berlandaskan <span class="italic text-secondary">Fitrah &amp; Sunnah</span>
</h1>
<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-10 max-w-2xl">
                        Membangun keunggulan akademik yang terintegrasi dengan nilai-nilai Islam yang murni, mempersiapkan generasi Rabbani untuk tantangan masa depan.
                    </p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Curriculum Integration Section -->
<section class="px-gutter py-section-padding-desktop bg-surface-container">
<div class="container mx-auto max-w-container-max">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center reveal active">
<div>
<span class="text-secondary font-label-caps mb-2 block">SISTEM PENDIDIKAN</span>
<h2 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-primary mb-6">Integrasi Kurikulum</h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-8 text-lg">Kami menyelaraskan standar pendidikan nasional dengan pondasi aqidah dan ilmu syar'i untuk menciptakan pendidikan yang utuh.</p>
<div class="space-y-6">
<div class="flex gap-4 p-6 bg-white rounded-lg border border-outline-variant">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">school</span>
<div>
<h4 class="font-bold text-primary mb-1">Kurikulum Merdeka</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">Pendekatan pembelajaran yang fleksibel, fokus pada materi esensial, dan pengembangan karakter melalui Profil Pelajar TS Lab School.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-4 p-6 bg-primary-container text-on-primary rounded-lg">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-tertiary-container text-3xl">menu_book</span>
<div>
<h4 class="font-bold text-white mb-1">TS Islamic Essential Knowledge</h4>
<p class="text-sm opacity-80">Kurikulum diniyah yang disusun sistematis mencakup Aqidah, Fiqih Ibadah, Sirah Nabawiyah, dan Adab harian sesuai Sunnah.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="relative">
<img alt="Books and natural elements" class="w-full h-[500px] object-cover rounded-lg shadow-xl" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCYE0DuFJMRFV-M7KlyvFajyP-dhZ2bdSIk3X9RtSdB1SF82xyf_Px4BMd-7fuB9Xlad2jUxymErTpvl6nuvtQFPIQXutZUqcX-bfMpnbhGqIDiZatWtuXHsF6lbFwQkolejPtd1Nf3eMIjOT9hyCYHNRpmYOJ6aIT86NNZ1Z3PpHoPzBNa5JWAujP6ZJu6b7mSSQDXgy_uBdWqTSIP7cjMEDrg_N8SUgQGy1GODS9nJRiQ9o0RnriyavHgeSiQwWFCRgm1eiy4_j0">
<div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-secondary p-8 rounded-lg text-on-secondary hidden md:block">
<p class="text-2xl font-display-lg italic">"Adab Sebelum Ilmu"</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Program Grid (Bento Style) -->
<section class="px-gutter py-section-padding-desktop bg-background relative">
<div class="pattern-overlay absolute inset-0"></div>
<div class="container mx-auto max-w-container-max relative z-10">
<div class="text-center mb-16">
<h2 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-primary mb-4">Program Unggulan</h2>
<div class="w-24 h-1 bg-secondary mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 stagger-reveal active">
<!-- Tahfizh -->
<div class="md:col-span-8 bg-surface border border-outline-variant p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm group hover:border-primary transition-colors transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-xl">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
<div class="w-full md:w-1/3">
<img alt="Quran and rehal" class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-DEFAULT" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBDNleoKYgIm8NZXh1GjaroaLxWHlUgqKpZeWa2A7bLaKqq3AgkkYRgO9-uP9SQ4-oMBRFRfpy5RiDJsL1A4nsFYRuphz03l4W585Bz5nN4yX-DEXjLUJntUKtSK0W3fjQEFY7bB_OInBhbxYLvuTFJhy9YVkJQhrB23MZ4Ss75TBBRAZK_U7Z4vgRfdbpZfoPiEzHE6QF9oDWiTpK6LWGTVyzNMIu7bCRxF-NMnAqu2AudmcJjq2VeJKQFLalg1UQ7W12tHwbl9W0">
</div>
<div class="w-full md:w-2/3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary mb-4 block">menu_book</span>
<h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-primary mb-3">Tahfizh Al-Qur'an</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">Program akselerasi hafalan dengan tajwid yang presisi dan pemahaman makna yang mendalam melalui metode Mutqin.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Organic Academic -->
<div class="md:col-span-4 bg-surface border border-outline-variant p-8 rounded-lg group hover:border-primary transition-colors transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-xl">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-secondary mb-4 block">eco</span>
<h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-primary mb-3">Organic Academic</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">Menyeimbangkan ketegasan akademik dengan lingkungan alami sebagai ruang kelas utama untuk eksplorasi.</p>
</div>
<!-- Modern Skills (Coding & Robotik) -->
<div class="md:col-span-4 bg-primary text-on-primary p-8 rounded-lg flex flex-col justify-between transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-xl">
<div>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-on-tertiary-container mb-6 block">precision_manufacturing</span>
<h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm mb-3">Coding &amp; Robotik</h3>
<p class="opacity-80">Mengenalkan logika pemrograman dan mekanika robotik sebagai bekal ketrampilan teknologi masa depan dengan panduan etika Islam.</p>
</div>
<div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-on-primary/20">
<p class="text-sm font-label-caps">MODERN SKILLS</p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Adab & Akhlak -->
<div class="md:col-span-4 bg-secondary-container p-8 rounded-lg flex flex-col items-center text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-xl">
<div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-on-secondary-container/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-on-secondary-container">account_balance</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-on-secondary-container mb-3">Adab &amp; Akhlak</h3>
<p class="text-on-secondary-container/80">Memprioritaskan pembentukan karakter islami dan kesantunan budi pekerti dalam setiap interaksi.</p>
</div>
<!-- Language Class -->
<div class="md:col-span-4 bg-surface border border-outline-variant p-8 rounded-lg group hover:border-primary transition-colors transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-xl">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary mb-4 block">translate</span>
<h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-primary mb-3">Kelas Bahasa</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">Penguasaan dua bahasa kunci (Arab &amp; Inggris) untuk membuka cakrawala keilmuan Islam dan global.</p>
</div>
<!-- Leadership & Kemandirian -->
<div class="md:col-span-6 bg-white p-10 rounded-lg border border-outline-variant flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-xl">
<div class="flex-1">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-secondary mb-4 block">groups</span>
<h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-primary mb-3">Leadership &amp; Kemandirian</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">Melatih jiwa kepemimpinan yang amanah serta kemandirian praktis melalui proyek tim dan tanggung jawab harian.</p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Bela Diri -->
<div class="md:col-span-6 bg-surface border border-outline-variant p-10 rounded-lg group hover:border-primary transition-colors flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-xl">
<div class="flex-1">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary mb-4 block">exercise</span>
<h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-primary mb-3">Bela Diri</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">Menguatkan fisik, kedisiplinan, dan keberanian melalui olahraga bela diri yang membentuk mental pejuang yang santun.</p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Islamic Science -->
<div class="md:col-span-12 bg-white p-12 rounded-lg border border-outline-variant flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 items-center transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-xl">
<div class="flex-1 order-2 md:order-1">
<h3 class="font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-primary mb-4">Sains Islami (Tadabbur Alam)</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-6 text-lg">Mempelajari fenomena alam sebagai ayat-ayat kauniyah yang mempertebal keimanan kepada Sang Pencipta.</p>
<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">check_circle</span>
<span class="font-medium">Observasi Lapangan</span>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">check_circle</span>
<span class="font-medium">Eksperimen Organik</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 order-1 md:order-2 w-full">
<img alt="Science lab setup" class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-lg shadow-lg" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAuZCUVRr9tvMIJQyJRx53N4QnfJ4eJgYY1a2_WNylIeZhCrJn58k2EklyhtPppVWoaG66lgWCm34j4uLvDxguiGF-aILuw5Jqna9gmPPFiXdK5ZarjJFlPqHt4gKma70LDYRva-Nt929HgLLodKQKN6CVk-_baBG65psWaIsoJlFxshZstVGZ6V6jCndfD5vE4_SfMjV45N4V2neUTppXhcOFtF6rqmgRoOcaB4ZNLDKelMXeHW9S5iSGCw0we_kOJQprPyOOI8Qk">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Extra-Curricular Activities -->
<section class="px-gutter py-section-padding-desktop bg-surface-container-low">
<div class="container mx-auto max-w-container-max">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-12 gap-6">
<div class="max-w-2xl">
<h2 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-primary mb-4">Kegiatan Ekstrakurikuler</h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">Mengasah bakat dan minat santri melalui kegiatan yang mendukung ketangkasan fisik, kepekaan seni, dan kecintaan pada literasi.</p>
</div>
<div class="hidden md:block">
<button class="flex items-center gap-2 text-primary font-bold hover:gap-4 transition-all">
                            Lihat Semua Jadwal <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_forward</span>
</button>
</div>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 stagger-reveal active">
<!-- Archery -->
<div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-surface group">
<div class="h-64 overflow-hidden">
<img alt="Archery range" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuC4Q6XCZ1-aXw76V8n3GFyG2fekB-G-m4BcmE3LxbEYDFSZDgi3rZKiW8Bptkchtj78RxHm-riz69sj0sVBwea9aUZOsrMzV2rJC9PK5zh08tWSarpvArBP7nAQIFqfgb0ymb88eLSr2l0ddD9upSF9xZBUtkckKqMc1j_B50sAeyLYgnWMpNb7eO3jslgImxqugZVlXzuSABoZIyCXnEFnuMDZaB2IPSDlfLkzGaW9WcOWXV8lHcsoMhwaXiO0vweqWtKt01BC3Pk">
</div>
<div class="p-8">
<div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-4">
<h4 class="font-headline-sm text-primary">Memanah</h4>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary">gps_fixed</span>
</div>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">Melatih fokus, konsentrasi, dan kesabaran melalui olahraga yang disunnahkan.</p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Gardening -->
<div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-surface group">
<div class="h-64 overflow-hidden">
<img alt="School garden" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuChFw-zF6FBoP04Ac_Dmc2saT5j3HZG0D3EvzgCF6CzzCeUBN8oZULaM0iFlMH7Sv4zHPARiuirIZNMdm1-V9L_YfwUB2qC654JHFk-8zgfJUY3IRNMCou8mTxG4OREC7Vwi3MBW9XB_1X2ZkpzieUVisBcl4fEN9e3H9oe5UM1nexoYCb5THx96Yg2u0EOQTCpNHeNrDiC3C4N8QN1WKg1LyJVxBZZavC0ObBmcFeqGMp0wUA8cuAPOMe3w28Je_8BFtba98kitwI">
</div>
<div class="p-8">
<div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-4">
<h4 class="font-headline-sm text-primary">Gardening</h4>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary">potted_plant</span>
</div>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">Menumbuhkan empati dan tanggung jawab melalui aktivitas berkebun organik.</p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Literacy Club -->
<div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-surface group">
<div class="h-64 overflow-hidden">
<img alt="Library corner" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCYE0DuFJMRFV-M7KlyvFajyP-dhZ2bdSIk3X9RtSdB1SF82xyf_Px4BMd-7fuB9Xlad2jUxymErTpvl6nuvtQFPIQXutZUqcX-bfMpnbhGqIDiZatWtuXHsF6lbFwQkolejPtd1Nf3eMIjOT9hyCYHNRpmYOJ6aIT86NNZ1Z3PpHoPzBNa5JWAujP6ZJu6b7mSSQDXgy_uBdWqTSIP7cjMEDrg_N8SUgQGy1GODS9nJRiQ9o0RnriyavHgeSiQwWFCRgm1eiy4_j0">
</div>
<div class="p-8">
<div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-4">
<h4 class="font-headline-sm text-primary">Literacy Club</h4>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary">history_edu</span>
</div>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">Membangun budaya membaca dan menulis yang kuat sebagai pemikir kritis.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- CTA Admissions -->
<section class="px-gutter py-section-padding-desktop">
<div class="container mx-auto max-w-container-max">
<div class="bg-primary-container rounded-xl p-8 md:p-16 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="pattern-overlay absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>
<div class="relative z-10">
<h2 class="font-display-lg text-display-lg-mobile md:text-display-lg text-white mb-6">Mulai Perjalanan Ilmu Ananda Bersama Kami</h2>
<p class="text-on-tertiary-container text-lg mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                            Penerimaan Santri Baru (SPMB) kini telah dibuka. Amankan kursi untuk masa depan pendidikan putra-putri Anda yang berbasis Sunnah dan fitrah.
                        </p>
<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
<button class="px-10 py-4 rounded-full bg-secondary text-on-secondary font-bold text-lg hover:scale-105 transition-transform">Daftar SPMB Online</button>
<a href="http://wa.me/6285173396002" class="px-10 py-4 rounded-full bg-white/10 text-white border border-white/20 font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors inline-block text-center">Konsultasi School Center</a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</main>
<!-- Floating Action Button Shell -->
<div class="fixed bottom-8 right-8 z-[60] flex items-center justify-center animate-bounce">
<a class="bg-secondary text-on-secondary rounded-full h-16 w-16 shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center hover:scale-110 transition-all" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">chat</span>
</a>
</div>
<script>
    const observerOptions = { threshold: 0.1 };
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
        entries.forEach(entry => {
            if (entry.isIntersecting) {
                entry.target.classList.add('active');
            }
        });
    }, observerOptions);

    document.querySelectorAll('.reveal, .stagger-reveal').forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
</script>


</Layout>
